<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Reset password</title>
		<style>
			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			body {
				font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
				font-size: 16px;
				line-height: 1.4;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}

			header {
				background-color: cornflowerblue;
				padding: 1em 2em;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: x-large;
				font-weight: bold;
			}

			.header-link {
				padding: 0.75em 1.5em;
				background-color: cornflowerblue;
				color: #fff;
				border: none;
				text-decoration: none;
				margin-bottom: 1em;
			}

			main {
				padding: 1em 2em;
			}

			.title {
				font-weight: bold;
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 1em;
				color: cornflowerblue;
			}

			.notify {
				color: steelblue;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: large;
			}

			.warning {
				font-size: large;
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
				color: rgb(221, 68, 51);
			}

			em {
				color: slateblue;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<a
				class="header-link"
				href="<%= home %>"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				>Weeb Forum</a
			>
		</header>
		<main>
			<h1 class="title">Reset Password</h1>

			<p class="notify">
				This mail is for reset password purpose. Please submit this OTP along
				with your new password in the reset password page.
			</p>

			<p>
				Konnichiwa, fellow Otaku: <em><strong><%= name %></strong></em>
			</p>

			<p>
				<em><strong>Your OTP:</strong> <%= OTP %></em>
			</p>

			<p>
				Thanking You <br />
				Your Tomo, <br />
				MailBot-kun ðŸ¤–
			</p>

			<p class="warning">
				<strong>Warning:</strong> Please don't share this OTP to anyone!
			</p>
			<p class="warning">
				<strong>Warning:</strong> This OTP will expire in 1 hour!
			</p>
			<p class="warning">
				<strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Please don't reply to this email. This is a
				system generated mail. You have received this mail because you're
				registered in Weeb Forum.
			</p>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
